{"tid":1230424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【毋須學聯】八間大專院校學生會呼籲市民明日參與罷工、罷市、罷課行動","createTime":"2019-06-16T07:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T13:35:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e9397e8e22318ea20d7b17469aa802092500f6f0","tid":1230424,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:38:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5d05e2d3e60383d378d32c4c/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5d05e2d3e60383d378d32c4c%2F&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=c40feb25\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5d05e2d3e60383d378d32c4c/</a><br />\n<br />\n八間大專院校學生會表示，政府暫緩《逃犯條例》修訂並未回應民意，號召明日罷課。<br />\n<br />\n中大、科大、浸大、城大、理大、教大、恒大及演藝學院學生會批評政府只是暫緩修例，而非撤回，亦未有收回對周三示威「暴動」的定性，表示遺憾及不能接受，呼籲市民明日參與罷工、罷市、罷課行動，若政府繼續不回應，不排除行動會升級。"},{"pid":"e5c80b8e154e45cd2a300f72f260df8050824654","tid":1230424,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:39:07.000Z","msg":"邊個再講要仆街學聯乜乜物物<br />\n<br />\n我就聯佢老母"},{"pid":"1601ef90c538ed427e348913ab02ac89f794cead","tid":1230424,"uid":229955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9hCJKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9hCJKF.jpg&h=0756c303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大會宣布 提前出發 @ 14:30 <br />\n<br />\n1) 由維園 去 金鐘添美道<br />\n2) 2 條 BANNER : 「痛心疾首」 「撤回惡法」 由宗教界 同 一班媽媽帶領<br />\n3) 「痛心疾首」 BANNER 會放喺適當地方 , 畀各市民獻花<br />\n4) 有宗教界負責安排 祈禱會<br />\n5) 有支援抗爭者基金籌款箱<br />\n<br />\n616 黑色大遊行 五大宗旨:<br />\n<br />\n1) 撒回惡法<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n2) 釋放被捕既抗爭者<br />\n3) 我們不是暴徒<br />\n4) 追究黑警開槍責任<br />\n5) 淋病下台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5667f91ed8aecc1ac6a6a69467e0572dac483509","tid":1230424,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}